
=== VoodooPHP ==

---------
- 5.3/1.1.0
July 19 2012
This version of Curl is backward incompatible
    * Voodoo\Core\HTTP\Curl
        - getResponse() return CurlResponse
        - call($METHOD) 
        - getHTTPCode()
        -> get($data), post($data)
    * Voodoo\Core\HTTP\CurlResponse
        - change jsonToArray to toArray()
        - removed httpCode(), to get the code use Core\Curl::getHTTPCode()
        - removed response()
        - added toString()
     * Voodoo\Paginator
        - Fix constant name
     * Voodoo\Forms
        - Simple form

---------
- 5.3/1.0.0
Friday July 13 2012
    - New versioning <PHPMajorVersion>.<PHPMinorVersion>/<VoodooMajor>.<VoodooMinor>.<VodooPatch>
    - PHP 5.3
    - Modular MVC
    - More setting in the module config
    - Dependency injection for views and pagination in the controller
